        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nWhile this looks good. The namespacing is all wrong. If you submit the template to global-jjb then the namespacing would be correct.\n\nWe need to keep things sanely namespaced so that if we find a particular macro / template that is useful to more than a one project we can lift it up to global-jjb without conflicts.",
